                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260622-227-off1161 t18260622-227-cd1162"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 2s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18260622-227-victim1206" type="victimName">
                        Andrew 
