               <p>ANDREW SPENCE. I am a <rs id="t18260622-227-viclabel1163" type="occupation">sailor</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260622-227-victim1206 t18260622-227-viclabel1163"></join>. I was close alongside of <placeName id="t18260622-227-crimeloc1164">Newgate</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260622-227-crimeloc1164" type="placeName" value="Newgate"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18260622-227-crimeloc1164" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260622-227-off1161 t18260622-227-crimeloc1164"></join> on the 16th of May, about ten or eleven o'clock - I had a handkerchief in my left pocket; I did not know I had lost it till it was given to me by a woman. The prisoner had run away, but was caught.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by Mr. PHILLIPS. Q. Is the woman here? A. No. This handkerchief is like mine, but it has been with others - I cannot swear it is the handkerchief the woman gave me.</p>
               <p>COURT. Q. Was the handkerchief given by the woman your's? A. Yes - I knew it at the time - there is no mark upon it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260622-227-person1207">
                  JOHN 
                  WRIGHT
               <interp inst="t18260622-227-person1207" type="surname" value="WRIGHT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260622-227-person1207" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260622-227-person1207" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a wine-merchant. I was going along Newgate-street on the 16th of May, and saw the prisoner take the handkerchief from the prosecutor, and put it into his own pocket; I informed the prosecutor, and kept my eye upon the prisoner, who, I think, observed me, for he dropped the handkerchief, and ran - I saw it picked up.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined. Q. Who picked it up? A. I do not know - I was more intent on watching the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I did not take it.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18260622-227-verdict1165" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18260622-227-verdict1165" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 20.</p>


